{
  "number": 54,
  "name": "سُورَةُ القَمَرِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Qamar",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "The Hour has come near, and the moon has split [in two].",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 528,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 211,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "And if they see a miracle, they turn away and say, \"Passing magic.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 528,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 211,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "And they denied and followed their inclinations. But for every matter is a [time of] settlement.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 528,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 211,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "And there has already come to them of information that in which there is deterrence -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 528,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 211,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "Extensive wisdom - but warning does not avail [them].",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 528,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 211,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "So leave them, [O Muhammad]. The Day the Caller calls to something forbidding,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 528,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 211,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Their eyes humbled, they will emerge from the graves as if they were locusts spreading,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 211,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "Racing ahead toward the Caller. The disbelievers will say, \"This is a difficult Day.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 211,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "The people of Noah denied before them, and they denied Our servant and said, \"A madman,\" and he was repelled.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "So he invoked his Lord, \"Indeed, I am overpowered, so help.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Then We opened the gates of the heaven with rain pouring down",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "And caused the earth to burst with springs, and the waters met for a matter already predestined.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "And We carried him on a [construction of] planks and nails,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Sailing under Our observation as reward for he who had been denied.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "And We left it as a sign, so is there any who will remember?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "And how [severe] were My punishment and warning.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "'Aad denied; and how [severe] were My punishment and warning.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "Indeed, We sent upon them a screaming wind on a day of continuous misfortune,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "Extracting the people as if they were trunks of palm trees uprooted.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "And how [severe] were My punishment and warning.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 463,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "Thamud denied the warning",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "And said, \"Is it one human being among us that we should follow? Indeed, we would then be in error and madness.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "Has the message been sent down upon him from among us? Rather, he is an insolent liar.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "They will know tomorrow who is the insolent liar.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "Indeed, We are sending the she-camel as trial for them, so watch them and be patient.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 529,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "And inform them that the water is shared between them, each [day of] drink attended [by turn].",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "But they called their companion, and he dared and hamstrung [her].",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And how [severe] were My punishment and warning.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "Indeed, We sent upon them one blast from the sky, and they became like the dry twig fragments of an [animal] pen.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "The people of Lot denied the warning.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "Indeed, We sent upon them a storm of stones, except the family of Lot - We saved them before dawn",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "As favor from us. Thus do We reward he who is grateful.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "And he had already warned them of Our assault, but they disputed the warning.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "And they had demanded from him his guests, but We obliterated their eyes, [saying], \"Taste My punishment and warning.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "And there came upon them by morning an abiding punishment.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "So taste My punishment and warning.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 464,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "And there certainly came to the people of Pharaoh warning.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "They denied Our signs, all of them, so We seized them with a seizure of one Exalted in Might and Perfect in Ability.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "Are your disbelievers better than those [former ones], or have you immunity in the scripture?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "Or do they say, \"We are an assembly supporting [each other]\"?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 45,
      "text": "[Their] assembly will be defeated, and they will turn their backs [in retreat].",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 46,
      "text": "But the Hour is their appointment [for due punishment], and the Hour is more disastrous and more bitter.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 47,
      "text": "Indeed, the criminals are in error and madness.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 48,
      "text": "The Day they are dragged into the Fire on their faces [it will be said], \"Taste the touch of Saqar.\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 49,
      "text": "Indeed, all things We created with predestination.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 530,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 50,
      "text": "And Our command is but one, like a glance of the eye.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 531,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 51,
      "text": "And We have already destroyed your kinds, so is there any who will remember?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 531,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 52,
      "text": "And everything they did is in written records.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 531,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 53,
      "text": "And every small and great [thing] is inscribed.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 531,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 54,
      "text": "Indeed, the righteous will be among gardens and rivers,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 531,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 55,
      "text": "In a seat of honor near a Sovereign, Perfect in Ability.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 531,
      "ruku": 465,
      "hizbQuarter": 212,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}